			date()

格式化日期 2011-01-07T12:22:11 各种用法常见于Java提供的接口

echo date("Y-m-d\TH:i:s", strtotime("2011-01-07 12:22:11"));			




			DateTime

$source = '2012-07-31';
$date = new DateTime($source);
echo $date->format('d.m.Y'); // 31.07.2012
echo $date->format('d-m-Y'); // 31-07-2012




			ISO 8601

echo date("Y-m-d\TH:i:s", strtotime("2011-01-07 12:22:11"));

echo date('c',time());

2016-08-23T16:01:08+08:00






